# Astrobloom

witness the pulse of life

## About
Astrobloom is a project that brings science and design together. Using NASA Earth observations, we detect plant blooming events around the worldâ€”just like pollinators do. Our mission is to make the hidden patterns of life on Earth visible, interactive, and useful.



